    This is a lambda that i created! The code within the lambda executes an alert box! It passed a string which is the customs message for the alert! My justification to using the alert for my lambda is because there are so many alerts and validation that needs to be checked and this lambda saves me a lot of time in code writing!

My justification to using the resultset for my lambda is because there are so queries that needs to be made and this lambda saves me a lot of time in code writing!

    ViewAppointmentsController
    This is the view appointments controller! This scene contains a tableview for all appointments! It also contains radio buttons if the user wants to view all appointments, weekly appointments or monthly appointments.
